Final Verdict

For the Sovereign Heritage Core, the Home PC should remain the "Master Vault." It ensures the integrity of the Data Pump and the long-term preservation of heavy files. The Mobile App should be marketed as the "Universal Key"—the beautiful interface that allows the user to manage their vault from anywhere in the world using their own biometrics.